 whole milk"},{"isHeader":false,"content":"50 g double cream"},{"isHeader":false,"content":"2 medium eggs"},{"isHeader":false,"content":"½ tsp fine sea salt"},{"isHeader":false,"content":"2 pinches ground black pepper"},{"isHeader":false,"content":"130 g smoked salmon, cut in pieces"}],"nutrition":["per 1 portion","1785 kJ \/ 427 kcal","22.2 g","28.4 g","24.9 g"],"hintsAndTricks":["It is traditional to brush the tops with melted butter before serving.","These small pots are deceptively filling. Makes a nice lunch option for when you want to impress - serve with a rocket salad.","A Swedish classic that is traditionally baked in one large pot. Here we've converted it to mini versions and steamed them in the Varoma!"],"basicInfo":["easy","10m","1h 10m","4 portions"]}